@LoveSync.IdentityGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5080

### Health
GET {{LoveSync.IdentityGateway_HostAddress}}/health

### Register
POST {{LoveSync.IdentityGateway_HostAddress}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana",
  "email": "ana@lovesync.dev",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123"
}

### Login
POST {{LoveSync.IdentityGateway_HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ana@lovesync.dev",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123"
}

### Pair (requires Bearer token from login)
POST {{LoveSync.IdentityGateway_HostAddress}}/auth/pair
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "invitationCode": "ABC12345"
}

### Gateway - Tasks (requires Bearer token)
GET {{LoveSync.IdentityGateway_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
